{"tid":1213948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.12 佔領成《時代》亞洲版封面　「香港在捍衛自由的戰爭前線」","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:37:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":102,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"545012fd0a9a94222b2fa811e624729144be09aa","tid":1213948,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/time-01_j2jrg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftime-01_j2jrg_1200x0.png&h=d344dfff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日的反送中運動演變成佔領金鐘，警方不斷施放催淚彈驅趕市民，現場煙霧彌漫。美國雜誌《時代》亞洲版最新一期封面為昨日「6.12 佔領」的照片，並以「抵抗（The Resistance）」為該期標題。《時代》更有一篇以「香港在一場捍衛自由的全球戰爭的前線」為題的文章，講述這次「6.12 佔領」的前因後果。 <br />\n<br />\n《時代》今日公布了將於 6 月 24 號發行的亞洲版雜誌封面 &mdash; 一把撐開的黑傘落在佔領街頭，旁邊的催淚煙仍未散去。該期標題為「抵抗（The Resistance）」。昨日下午，警方向佔領金鐘的民眾施放大量催淚彈、胡椒噴霧，民眾打開雨傘阻擋，但大批催淚煙襲來時，大家紛紛棄傘逃亡。《時代》雜誌這張封面照便是攝於那煙霧瀰漫的瞬間，拍下那一把被落下的黑傘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ezgif.com-webp-to-jpg_fYx66_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fezgif.com-webp-to-jpg_fYx66_1200x0.jpg&h=962d0794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《時代》文章「香港在一場捍衛自由的全球戰爭的前線（Hong Kong Is On the Frontlines of a Global Battle For Freedom）」，指這次反送中運動是香港 1997 年主權移交以來最大規模的一次民眾上街抗議行動。 文章又強調，香港人長期生活在一個比中國更自由、國際化的環境，並對於自己的文化、語言（廣東話）感到自豪，然而很多評論者都擔心中國的介入將中間香港的言論自由、新聞自由及獨有文化。前美國外交人員 Sean King 亦表示「若《逃犯條例》（修訂）變成法律，我會三思之後是否要再去香港。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-佔領成-時代-亞洲版封面-香港在捍衛自由的戰爭前線/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E6%88%90-%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%89%88%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%A8%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%2F&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmghG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=09e0e338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-12-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E6%88%90-%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%89%88%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%A8%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%2F&h=cf45135c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-12-佔領成-時代-亞洲版封面-香港在捍衛自由的戰爭前線/</a>"},{"pid":"1da5cc73b5ef45fb15ea9744f39773d09f9b25b7","tid":1213948,"uid":3135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7ceb1f52998ba45e9fdaa2ef36132de55f43422","tid":1213948,"uid":73281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:15:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5970c7b6a3dc16aa74f819117fd924335cffbfcb","tid":1213948,"uid":199257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"全世界睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24984bd27f6acd8671df162e65898129f3fcb15","tid":1213948,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e93785715929e2624070d7dfd61b1aaf5d74b4a","tid":1213948,"uid":254330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"國際關注呀"},{"pid":"eff4ffa82ba62d618bcade09717cd36edd4fd6da","tid":1213948,"uid":145690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"推 比世界更多人見到 港人要自由既決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c1e7a32e74333350efc9e3f6e77e0f51122e78","tid":1213948,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14040ef6832f7c65f1314064b3741cd533f99525","tid":1213948,"uid":238613,"like":1,"dislike":0